OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK aid spending on asylum  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fseekers rises again        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than a quarter of all UK overseas 
OL,6, aid was spent on asylum costs at home  
OL,7, last year, new figures show.           
OL,9,FThe Foreign Office statistics reveal   
OL,10,F#4.3bn of its foreign aid budget went  
OL,11,Fon supporting refugees and asylum      
OL,12,Fseekers in the UK.                     
OL,14,FThat represents a 16% increase from the
OL,15,F#3.7bn that was spent in 2022.         
OL,17,FCritics say the government has "lost   
OL,18,Fits grip" by allowing the Home Office  
OL,19,Fto use UK foreign aid budgets,         
OL,20,Fweakening crisis prevention schemes.   
